and that’s how I have surrendered myself to Him.” It’s wrong.

00:45:03.000 --> 00:45:07.892
You cannot do it, because you have got ego. You have to cross beyond.

00:45:08.000 --> 00:45:12.892
Unless and until you cross behind – beyond, you cannot get over your ego.

00:45:13.000 --> 00:45:19.892
So these ego and superego, if you see, they cross. So the superego is, say, from here to here.

00:45:20.000 --> 00:45:21.892
The ego is from here to here.

00:45:22.000 --> 00:45:26.892
But as the human beings started growing the superego which is the conditioning in us,

00:45:27.000 --> 00:45:31.892
the conditioning as seen by the psychologists, they call it the psyche part

00:45:32.000 --> 00:45:34.892
and they never realised that there is also ego.

00:45:35.000 --> 00:45:38.892
If you remove the conditionings completely from human beings, do whatever you please,

00:45:39.000 --> 00:45:43.892
you become egoistical. They never realised this subtle point

00:45:44.000 --> 00:45:52.892
and they allowed you to do whatever you liked, and they allowed you to, sort of fully assert yourself.

00:45:53.000 --> 00:45:58.892
Then they did never realise that on the other side is also this ego developing within you.

00:45:59.000 --> 00:46:03.892
And that’s why we have got now countries we can say which are ego-oriented.

00:46:04.000 --> 00:46:06.892
Others are superego-oriented.

00:46:07.000 --> 00:46:18.892
But now the stage is such that nothing much to choose, it’s such a confusion and a muddle.

00:46:19.000 --> 00:46:25.892
they tried to push the superego down like that which went to such a limit that it started hurting people.

00:46:26.000 --> 00:46:29.892
They couldn’t bear it so they came up with their superego.

00:46:30.000 --> 00:46:36.892
And this is the beginning of people talking about, “I feel very guilty,” “I’m very sorry,”

00:46:37.000 --> 00:46:39.892
“We must have some sympathy for others,”

00:46:40.000 --> 00:46:44.892
“We must look after the people who are suffering,” and all that kind of a thing.

00:46:45.000 --> 00:46:53.892
Then they take to also drugs. Also you can see that all this left side is more sort of meant for people

00:46:54.000 --> 00:47:00.892
who take drugs and who go into lethargy and more sitting down and dreaming for poets, all sorts of things.

00:47:01.000 --> 00:47:01.892
[Missing part]

00:47:02.000 --> 00:47:06.892
went to India and invaded India and now I am responsible for that.

00:47:07.000 --> 00:47:17.892
You start feeling guilty for somebody who’s died and is born somewhere in Africa or maybe born in Timbuktu.

00:47:18.000 --> 00:47:20.892
You see maybe that you are the one who was a saint in India

00:47:21.000 --> 00:47:27.892
and who has been looked after the Mother and today you are here crying for nothing at all.

00:47:28.000 --> 00:47:33.892
So this is the situation of today’s muddled-up world and the superego,

00:47:34.000 --> 00:47:37.892
or the others who were supposed to be superego, non-aggressive people,

00:47:38.000 --> 00:47:43.892
say like Indian people, now are, they are developing, they are getting sophisticated, you see.

00:47:44.000 --> 00:47:46.892
And they think that to wear a suit is a very big thing.

00:47:47.000 --> 00:47:49.892
If you wear a suit they start speaking some other language.

00:47:50.000 --> 00:47:57.892
And to them you see to be posh, to be very impressive and all that is very important.

00:47:58.000 --> 00:48:02.892
Whether they have food or not doesn’t matter but must dress up well to impress people,

00:48:03.000 --> 00:48:07.892
you see, and that’s why I tell always my disciples that when you go to India don’t go like hippies.

00:48:08.000 --> 00:48:13.892
Better go like very well-dressed government servants. And you can only impress them only….

00:48:14.000 --> 00:48:21.892
And there, so we are developing now in India and we are becoming very materialistic, extremely materialistic.

00:48:22.000 --> 00:48:26.892
I mean not that you people here in the West have left your materialism to that extent

00:48:27.000 --> 00:48:30.892
but I mean here every Dick, Tom and Harry is not a materialistic person.

00:48:31.000 --> 00:48:35.892
Specially the people who are of a higher style, they are not that materialistic.

00:48:36.000 --> 00:48:40.892
But like, your, you see, the labor class here you can say as they are very particular now…

00:48:41.000 --> 00:48:44.892
Today was the budget day, last day

00:48:45.000 --> 00:48:48.892
so all the shops were on and everybody was buying even the jewellery?, then everything,

00:48:49.000 --> 00:48:52.892
in the shops, you see. But the Indians would be the most, you see,

00:48:53.000 --> 00:48:57.892
because they must see what is happening here. As soon as… I wouldn’t say Indians,

00:48:58.000 --> 00:49:01.892
all the Asians I would put like that, not only Indians,

00:49:02.000 --> 00:49:06.892
because you see when they come to England they see in the shops, you see.

00:49:07.000 --> 00:49:08.892
They make the list of saris they have to take home.

00:49:09.000 --> 00:49:11.892
They make the list of things they have to take home.

00:49:12.000 --> 00:49:15.892
They are equally the same as you have been long time back.

00:49:16.000 --> 00:49:21.892
Like you’ll be amazed that once upon a time plastic was a big, big craze for you people here

00:49:22.000 --> 00:49:27.892
and nylon was also once upon a time. Now we are trying to wear nylons for you.

00:49:28.000 --> 00:49:33.892
It’s a good exchange, I think, but this is what we are in the muddle, either in the superego or ego.

00:49:34.000 --> 00:49:38.892
We cannot just fix the person. He could be one moment in the superego, one moment in the ego.

00:49:39.000 --> 00:49:41.892
He’ll be just going from one side to another.

00:49:42.000 --> 00:49:49.892
The thing that really gives you the balance is the sustenance, is the sustenance, dharma.

00:49:50.000 --> 00:50:03.892
If you do not have that then you could go, shoot off like a pendulum from this side to that.

00:50:04.000 --> 00:50:10.892
So I mean if you try to make the dharma a fanatic idea like none of these incarnations,

00:50:11.000 --> 00:50:15.892
like Mohamed Sahib who was an incarnation of the Primordial Master

00:50:16.000 --> 00:50:20.892
and all others like Him – Moses, Abraham – anyone of Them who came on this earth,

00:50:21.000 --> 00:50:26.892
ever thought of fanaticism. Never they realised that when they told,

00:50:27.000 --> 00:50:31.892
“Don’t do this. Don’t do that,” some sort of people will take up upon themselves that,

00:50:32.000 --> 00:50:38.892
“We are the chosen ones. We are the great.” I mean, this they could have never understood

00:50:39.000 --> 00:50:41.892
and whenever they found it was happening again they took birth.

00:50:42.000 --> 00:50:45.892
Again they took birth to tell people this is not dharma.

00:50:46.000 --> 00:50:53.892
To form any kind of a cult or an organisation and religion is against God. It’s blasphemous.

00:50:54.000 --> 00:50:56.892
How can you organise God? You cannot.

00:50:57.000 --> 00:51:02.892
Those who have done it always have brought absolute fall of human beings. You see,

00:51:03.000 --> 00:51:04.892
that’s why you cannot control. Like the other day I was saying

00:51:05.000 --> 00:51:08.892
that our Pope has good intentions of going to Poland.

00:51:09.000 --> 00:51:13.892
But in a way I like Polish Catholicism more than the Irish one.

00:51:14.000 --> 00:51:19.892
If this is the freedom what Catholicism is, better not have it.

00:51:20.000 --> 00:51:23.892
You see, if this is what you are going to achieve through your Catholicism, better not have it.

00:51:24.000 --> 00:51:28.892
In Poland, say, for example, people do not do philanthropic work, you see,

00:51:29.000 --> 00:51:33.892
like helping the poor. Is that the work of Christ? I asked somebody, I said,

00:51:34.000 --> 00:51:38.892
“How did you come to this conclusion that Christ wanted you to help the poor?”

00:51:39.000 --> 00:51:41.892
They said, “Because You know once He was to be,

00:51:42.000 --> 00:51:49.892
He was to be anointed with some very expensive oil,” and I think Judah said that

00:51:50.000 --> 00:51:55.892
‘How can you spend such a lot of money on Him, on His body?

00:51:56.000 --> 00:51:57.892
Let us sell it and give it to the poor.'”

00:51:58.000 --> 00:52:04.892
So He said – now, see, listen to this one carefully – He said that, “Poor are forever,”

00:52:05.000 --> 00:52:08.892
means it’s a permanent headache, you see, “but I am for a short time.”

00:52:09.000 --> 00:52:13.892
That means spiritual life is the thing. Now, in the same way He said that

00:52:14.000 --> 00:52:17.892
“No rich man can enter into the kingdom of God.”

00:52:18.000 --> 00:52:21.892
Both are just the same. Poor are just the same as the rich. Do you find any difference in them?

00:52:22.000 --> 00:52:34.892
I do not. One hankers after money; another one gets spoilt by it.

00:52:35.000 --> 00:52:40.892
and one has, that’s why he is no good. If the rich had little less money it would be better for them.

00:52:41.000 --> 00:52:42.892
And if the poor had little more it would be better.

00:52:43.000 --> 00:52:48.892
So our Sahaja Yoga works for the people of the middle, middle things.

00:52:49.000 --> 00:52:52.892
Now immediately you will say, “Then what about the poor of the world?”

00:52:53.000 --> 00:52:55.892
Immediately the attention will go there. “Mother, what do you think?”

00:52:56.000 --> 00:52:58.892
Now you don’t worry about that part.

00:52:59.000 --> 00:53:05.892
There is God who has created them and He is going to look after them. Are you an economist?

00:53:06.000 --> 00:53:09.892
Then you are, you have done all bad things.

00:53:10.000 --> 00:53:14.892
Because of faulty planning, because of selfish nature, because of conservatism,

00:53:15.000 --> 00:53:18.892
because of thinking that you are the person who should enjoy all your wealth,

00:53:19.000 --> 00:53:22.892
you have created these disparities. Human beings have created, not God,

00:53:23.000 --> 00:53:27.892
and when you have to achieve God you don’t have to think all these problems that human beings have created.

00:53:28.000 --> 00:53:30.892
Like somebody came and told Me, “What about Vietnam?” I said,

00:53:31.000 --> 00:53:37.892
“Are you a governor appointed there?” You see, he had a problem of his own.

00:53:38.000 --> 00:53:41.892
He was coming from an asylum and he asked Me, gets up very seriously, said,

00:53:42.000 --> 00:53:44.892
“What about Vietnam?” Now tell Me, this fellow is really half mad.

00:53:45.000 --> 00:53:49.892
He’s gone to that asylum from where he has come, and why is he worried about this Vietnam?

00:53:50.000 --> 00:53:54.892
Now, what does that show? How is he going to help Vietnam?

00:53:55.000 --> 00:53:57.892
This is how the attention of human beings moves. I mean,

00:53:58.000 --> 00:54:01.892
what you have to do is to achieve that within yourself, your own powers.

00:54:02.000 --> 00:54:09.892
Everyone has to achieve that power. Even if you are poor you can achieve it. What is poverty?

00:54:10.000 --> 00:54:13.892
It’s just mental idea, “It is poverty.” You see, for people I’ve seen,

00:54:14.000 --> 00:54:21.892
horrible people who are supposed to be rich just like beggars, I tell you, absolutely beggars.

00:54:22.000 --> 00:54:29.892
Even if they could get out of you one torn handkerchief, oh, they will be very happy.

00:54:30.000 --> 00:54:34.892
Horrible people, I don’t know, what riches, it has not gone even skin deep.

00:54:35.000 --> 00:54:42.892
Even I would tell you that if you put so many pounds just posted on a donkey

00:54:43.000 --> 00:54:47.892
he would look better than these people are. I mean, it has not touched them at all, you see.

00:54:48.000 --> 00:54:52.892
And the way they talk you know how the people are, how licentious they are,

00:54:53.000 --> 00:54:55.892
how permissive they are, how careless they are about their children,

00:54:56.000 --> 00:55:02.892
how they are irresponsible, how they are killing others just to save their reputation.

00:55:03.000 --> 00:55:05.892
I mean, there’s nothing that they cannot do.

00:55:06.000 --> 00:55:08.892
Same with poorer people; they are just the same. You see,

00:55:09.000 --> 00:55:12.892
if you go and talk to them, now our Maria had this, this thing, they said,

00:55:13.000 --> 00:55:18.892
“We, we want this man to be cured by Mataji but we are not going to believe in God.”

00:55:19.000 --> 00:55:25.892
Now what can you say to that? Only you can say to take two running jumps and go to hell.

00:55:26.000 --> 00:55:27.892
That’s what it is meant for such horrible people.

00:55:28.000 --> 00:55:31.892
They want to take advantage of God’s power and then, “We don’t believe in God.”

00:55:32.000 --> 00:55:39.892
See, this is poverty. And the poorer they are the worse they are in their arrogance,

00:55:40.000 --> 00:55:43.892
in their assertions, in their asking. They don’t want to do any work.

00:55:44.000 --> 00:55:45.892
They want to have this. They want to have that.

00:55:46.000 --> 00:55:42.892
All these things will be only explained once they achieve God. Otherwise they will not move.

00:55:43.000 --> 00:56:02.892
They all must rise. I mean, that the way the churches have now become nothing but union offices,

00:56:03.000 --> 00:56:10.892
labor union offices. See, poor people go there and confess to the priest. Now, it’s madness.

00:56:11.000 --> 00:56:13.892
He cannot do anything to them. What is he after all?

00:56:14.000 --> 00:56:18.892
He himself is an ordinary human being, ordained. Which by whom?

00:56:19.000 --> 00:56:21.892
God has ordained you? Or who has ordained you?

00:56:22.000 --> 00:56:29.892
All such organisations will only create headaches and people who have got nothing

00:56:30.000 --> 00:56:34.892
but some sort of an idea that they are something great. You see, you ask anyone,

00:56:35.000 --> 00:56:40.892
“What are you?” “I’m a Catholic.” What does that mean? “I’m a,” what you call that,

00:56:41.000 --> 00:56:43.892
“Church of England.” In India specially, the Indian Christians,

00:56:44.000 --> 00:56:51.892
if somebody is from Church of England he will not look at the person from Church of Scotland.

00:56:52.000 --> 00:56:56.892
You should see Indians, you see when they are Christians you must see the way they are.

00:56:57.000 --> 00:56:58.892
“Oh, we, we don’t talk to them.” I said, “Why?”

00:56:59.000 --> 00:57:01.892
“Because they are from the Church of Scotland, you know,”

00:57:02.000 --> 00:57:04.892
or Presbyterians you see, or Lutherans. So according to them

00:57:05.000 --> 00:57:06.892
they are the highest because Church of England.

00:57:07.000 --> 00:57:10.892
Now they must come and see the condition of Church of England to understand. You see,

00:57:11.000 --> 00:57:19.892
this is the trouble. It is really, I tell you, like lunatic people. It’s absolutely like lunatic people.

00:57:20.000 --> 00:57:24.892
They are brainwashed, completely. And by that they are not going to achieve anything.

00:57:25.000 --> 00:57:28.892
We have to achieve the reality. We have to know that we have to achieve it

00:57:29.000 --> 00:57:32.892
and for that we have to stand by reality, face it moment and moment

00:57:33.000 --> 00:57:39.892
and then the enjoyment of reality will be uncovered and will be absolutely manifested within you.

00:57:40.000 --> 00:57:44.892
But we have to stand by reality and not go by thinking, “I think, Mataji, You were wrong there.”

00:57:45.000 --> 00:57:46.892
I said, “Where? Where was I wrong?”

00:57:47.000 --> 00:57:50.892
“Because, You know, You told us this,” and that’s why I was wrong.

00:57:51.000 --> 00:57:52.892
I said, “How do you know?” “I feel that way.”

00:57:53.000 --> 00:57:56.892
“Now, how can you feel about what I am thinking or what I am saying?

00:57:57.000 --> 00:58:02.892
You have to then understand rationally. But when I say rationally, do you understand?”

00:58:03.000 --> 00:58:04.892
“Rationally I understand but I don’t feel that way.”

00:58:05.000 --> 00:58:09.892
Now, what is this feel? See, a thing which is told to you rationally must be understood rationally.

00:58:10.000 --> 00:58:13.892
And whatever is to be felt is to be felt through heart.

00:58:14.000 --> 00:58:21.892
But they will feel a rational thing and they will think about the love. It is something absurd.

00:58:22.000 --> 00:58:25.892
That’s why it is crazy. The attitude itself is crazy.

00:58:26.000 --> 00:58:29.892
So open out yourself because there is an invitation.

00:58:30.000 --> 00:58:36.892
There is a great invitation for you to enter into that kingdom of God which is promised to you.

00:58:37.000 --> 00:58:42.892
You must know that God has created this earth. He has created you.

00:58:43.000 --> 00:58:47.892
He is not going to allow His creation to be destroyed, will He? What are you worried about?

00:58:48.000 --> 00:58:51.892
He is the One who is going to take you across.

00:58:52.000 --> 00:58:54.892
He is the One who is going to tell you each and everything that He has,

00:58:55.000 --> 00:58:58.892
to possess all the beauties, all the blessings that He has,

00:58:59.000 --> 00:59:02.892
to enjoy them. He is going to do everything for you.

00:59:03.000 --> 00:59:06.892
But when the boat is crossing, keep quiet. Don’t run here and there.

00:59:07.000 --> 00:59:10.892
All the time the children are running from here and there. You go on catching them.

00:59:11.000 --> 00:59:14.892
“Come along. Come along.” Sometimes even they get drowned. Just keep quiet.

00:59:15.000 --> 00:59:20.892
Everybody is going to get it, everybody is going to be taken into it and everybody is going to enjoy it.

00:59:21.000 --> 00:59:25.892
For today I think it was quite a lecture though I have told you

00:59:26.000 --> 00:59:30.892
that Christ is on this chakra has come and that is the last chakra of Sahasrara

00:59:31.000 --> 00:59:40.892
which opened on the fifth of May in India in 1970

00:59:41.000 --> 00:59:48.892
and since then the new awareness has started becoming, dawning into people.

00:59:49.000 --> 00:59:52.892
The vibrations have started flowing. And it’s a very great thing that you are born at this time

00:59:53.000 --> 00:59:55.892
and you are the people, the foundations.

00:59:56.000 --> 00:59:58.892
You are the people who are going to receive it completely.

00:59:59.000 --> 01:00:01.892
I don’t know about the future, what is going to happen to the future and all that

01:00:02.000 --> 01:00:06.892
but I am sure it is going to work out. And in this London,

01:00:07.000 --> 01:00:11.892
London which I have always said it’s the heart of the universe, we are going to do it

01:00:12.000 --> 01:00:15.892
with great understanding of the problems of the whole world.

01:00:16.000 --> 01:00:20.892
If heart is all right everything will be all right because through it everything is going to circulate,

01:00:21.000 --> 01:00:26.892
and going to improve, and going to nurture, and going to develop this beautiful universe

01:00:27.000 --> 01:00:32.892
that God has created for you. But first thing you must know is to give up all your misidentifications.

01:00:33.000 --> 01:00:39.892
And do not go on hankering onto them and again getting identifying yourself with them

01:00:40.000 --> 01:00:46.892
but keep a complete alert attention on your progress in Sahaja Yoga.

01:00:47.000 --> 01:00:51.892
I’m sure it is going to work out. May God bless you all! Thank you.

01:01:04.000 --> 01:01:13.892
So, any questions?

01:01:14.000 --> 01:01:19.892
Now, ask questions which are related to this lecture.

01:01:20.000 --> 01:01:22.892
Because if you ask them out of the blue questions, you see

01:01:23.000 --> 01:01:26.892
not out of the blue questions, see what is there, now I need another lecture.

01:01:27.000 --> 01:01:30.892
You see, I cannot just say what is God is and things like that.

01:01:31.000 --> 01:01:32.892
So you please don’t ask such questions.

01:01:33.000 --> 01:01:37.892
Ask something relating to this lecture that would help you and everybody.

01:01:38.000 --> 01:01:40.892
And ask questions which are constructive.

