Now you think of that thought. You see,

01:03:30.000 --> 01:03:32.892
now you cannot. Can you?  Try.

01:03:44.000 --> 01:03:50.892
No, no. That is the fact. One must accept. You have crossed the Agnya.

01:03:51.000 --> 01:03:56.892
You see, now you cannot. Enjoy it. Enjoy it. It’s very good.

