Good. This is very beautiful.

01:04:19.000 --> 01:04:20.892
Enjoy it. Forget it.

01:04:21.000 --> 01:04:27.892
Forget about that. We are going to meet again and again and you’ll have ample time.

01:04:28.000 --> 01:04:31.892
But the more you will be meeting the more you’ll become thoughtless,

01:04:32.000 --> 01:04:33.892
the more you’ll be enjoying the silence within you,

01:04:34.000 --> 01:04:37.892
more you will be going deep into your own silence, really enjoying it.

01:04:38.000 --> 01:04:41.892
Actually after Realisation you don’t even feel bored. You’ll be surprised.

01:04:42.000 --> 01:04:45.892
You’ll be sitting for hours together without getting bored, absolutely without getting bored.

01:04:46.000 --> 01:04:50.892
And that’s how people give up, you see, all these habits of say, smoking and all those

01:04:51.000 --> 01:04:54.892
because when you are bored you don’t know what to do so you take to these habits.

01:04:55.000 --> 01:04:57.892
That’s what you get it. You are not to be forced, you are not to be told

01:04:58.000 --> 01:05:01.892
but once you start enjoying yourself you just don’t do it. [Hindi]

